---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>🧍 Characters</h1>
    <p>Track the characters that bring your world to life — from brave adventurers to mysterious NPCs.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>🧙 Player Characters (PCs)</h2>
      <p>These are the main characters controlled by your players. As your campaign unfolds, they’ll evolve, level up, and change the story forever.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create detailed character sheets</li>
        <li>Upload portraits or custom art</li>
        <li>Track stats, gear, spells, goals, and more</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🏘️ NPCs & Story Characters</h2>
      <p>Populate your world with vibrant townsfolk, terrifying villains, and helpful questgivers.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Organize NPCs by location, faction, or story arc</li>
        <li>Add secret GM-only notes</li>
        <li>Track relationships with the party</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🤝 Allies & Retainers</h2>
      <p>Not quite NPCs, not quite party members — these companions help (or hinder) your group in unique ways.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Assign roles: healer, scout, moral compass, etc.</li>
        <li>Track loyalty or influence</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
